Package org.red5.codec

Interface IEnhancedRTMPVideoCodec

All Superinterfaces:
IVideoStreamCodec
All Known Implementing Classes:
HEVCVideo
public interface IEnhancedRTMPVideoCodec extends IVideoStreamCodec
Extended interface for new E-rtmp video handlers. Methods called by abstract video codec when allowing it to parse the data. Methods are called only if codec id of frame is valid.
Author:
mondain
